---
import DefaultLayout from '@/layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';
import { Background } from '@/components/background';
import { AnimatedGrid } from '@/components/animated-grid';
---

<DefaultLayout title="About - Hooklyne" description="We built the research layer we wished existed. Between cheap contact databases and expensive agencies.">
  <Background>
    <AnimatedGrid client:only="react" />
    <section class="py-28 lg:py-32 lg:pt-48">
      <div class="container max-w-4xl">

        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-[#344ca3]/20 bg-[#344ca3]/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#344ca3] uppercase tracking-wide">
            About us
          </span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-[#022f51] text-4xl tracking-tight md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-6">
          We got tired of the same problem.
        </h1>

        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 mb-12">
          <div>
            <p class="text-[#64748b] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Both of us work in B2B sales. We've seen the same thing at every company: the research takes longer than the outreach. You spend hours finding the right company, finding the right person, figuring out what to say - and by the time you're ready, the moment has passed.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[#64748b] text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The choice was always the same: spend 30 minutes researching each prospect and send 10 great emails, or skip the research and blast 200 templates. Neither worked.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[#64748b] text-base leading-relaxed">
              The tools that exist either give you raw data and expect you to do the work, or they're built for enterprise teams with SDR armies and six-figure contracts. There was nothing in the middle - nothing that worked for a 15-person Dutch company with two sales reps and a full pipeline to manage.
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* Image placeholder - about hero */}
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-[#f8fafc] min-h-[280px] flex items-center justify-center">
            <p class="text-xs text-[#64748b]/50 text-center px-4">Replace with founders photo - casual setting, whiteboard or laptop visible</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-[#e2e8f0] pt-12 mb-12">
          <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#022f51] mb-2">So we built it.</p>
          <p class="text-[#64748b] text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            Today, Hooklyne finds the real reason to reach out, verifies the contact, and writes the outreach in your voice. Your team reviews and sends. That's it.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Founders */}
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 mb-14">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-white p-6 flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div class="size-14 rounded-2xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-[#f1f5f9] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[#022f51]">J</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-center text-[#64748b] text-[10px] mt-1">Replace with photo</p>
            </div>
            <div>
    
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-white p-6 flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div class="size-14 rounded-2xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-[#f1f5f9] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[#344ca3]">T</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-center text-[#64748b] text-[10px] mt-1">Replace with photo</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[#022f51] font-semibold text-base mb-0.5">Tim</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-[#344ca3] font-medium mb-2">Co-founder</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#64748b] leading-relaxed">Sales background deep in Dutch B2B account development. Knows exactly how Dutch buyers think and what makes outreach land - or get ignored.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* What we believe */}
        <div class="mb-14">
          <h2 class="text-[#022f51] text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">What we believe</h2>
          <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            {[
              { title: "Quality over quantity", body: "Call 5 prepared, don't blast 1,000. The best outreach is specific, timely, and relevant - not a numbers game. Hooklyne is built around this principle." },
              { title: "Outreach should sound like you", body: "Generic templates get ignored. We write in your voice, referencing real signals about the prospect. It takes more to build - but the results speak for themselves." },
              { title: "Dutch B2B deserves better tooling", body: "Most sales intelligence tools are built for the US market, in English, for enterprise teams. The Dutch SME market has been underserved. We're fixing that." },
              { title: "You shouldn't need to interpret data", body: "Tools that give you a data dump and expect you to figure it out aren't saving you time. Hooklyne delivers finished work - not raw intelligence to analyse." },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-white p-5 flex gap-3">
                <div class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-[#ff8c42] shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#022f51] mb-1">{item.title}</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-[#64748b] leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Stats */}
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-14 rounded-2xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-white p-6">
          {[
            { v: "4", l: "Intelligence sources" },
            { v: "20+", l: "Data providers" },
            { v: "EN + NL", l: "From day one" },
          ].map((s) => (
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#022f51]">{s.v}</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-[#64748b] mt-1">{s.l}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        {/* CTA */}
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#344ca3]/20 bg-[#022f51] p-8 text-center text-white">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">We're running a pilot</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
            10 fully researched prospect packages, all features included, in exchange for a feedback call. No credit card.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-white text-[#022f51] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          >
            Request pilot access
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </Background>
</DefaultLayout>
